headline: ROLLINS, INC. ANNOUNCES REGULAR QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, announced that the Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.165 per share payable June 10, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on May 12, 2025.

headline: Independent Analysis Shows Imagine360 Saved Rollins, Inc. Nearly 20% Compared to Traditional Health Plans
summary: Imagine360, a leading alternative health plan for self-funded employers, released results from an independent analysis conducted by Axene Health Partners finding that through Imagine360, Rollins, Inc. (NYSE:ROL) experienced approximately 19% savings—approximately $7.7 million annually—compared to traditional health plans. In addition to significant savings, Rollins health plan members reported a great experience with Imagine360, including a 90% satisfaction score and a 99% claims acceptance rate
